Key Stats: 
‚Äî iPhone 16 lead times in the US are down 33% Y/Y, currently at 14.4 days, compared to 21.6 days for the iPhone 15 at this stage last year. 
 
‚Äî iPhone 16 Pro Max lead times are 22.5 days in the US, down from 18 days for the iPhone 15 Pro Max and 14 days for the iPhone 14 Pro Max.
